data.description: Mountain Retreat with Stunning Views and Mid-Century Charm  Welcome to your mountain retreat nestled in the serene surroundings of Arrowhead Woods.  This property offers a unique blend of natural beauty, architectural style, and modern comforts.  Immerse yourself in the beauty of nature as this home is enveloped by towering trees. The lush greenery provides a sense of tranquility and privacy, creating a peaceful oasis for you to escape the city.  This home showcases the timeless elegance of mid-century design, with its clean lines, open floor plan, and seamless integration with nature.  As you step inside this near level entry home you'll immediately notice the soaring windows and a warm and inviting interior.   The living room opens to the bright dining room kitchen. Convenience is key with this home as the primary bedroom and full bath are also on the entry level.  Step onto the back deck off the dining area and you'll be greeted by breathtaking views of the majestic mountain ridge lines in the distance.  Whether it's enjoying your morning coffee to the sounds of nature and a sunrise view, or hosting a gathering with friends, you'll want to return again and again to this picturesque backdrop.  Downstairs there is a family gathering space with 2 more bedrooms, another full bath, and a large utility/laundry room.  When you purchase this home, you'll have coveted lake rights, granting you access to the myriad of recreational activities that privately owned Lake Arrowhead has to offer.  From boating, water skiing, fishing, beautiful walking trails, and lakeside picnics, there's something for everyone to enjoy.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this gorgeous retreat your mountain home.
